juices.description: Dessert lover? Love Strawberry Shortcake? this is the one for you!

Boston Cream captures every nuance of a Boston Cream doughnut.  The inhale greets you with a fresh baked doughnut taste, then the exhale erupts into the full spectrum of Boston Cream:  A fresh baked doughnut with a chocolate glaze accent, complemented by a rich and creamy filling and a hint of powdered sugar to top it off.
Crystallized gummi worms laced  with psychedelic sweet tarts

POTUS wants you to stop listening to science. The sun hasn’t died…it’s alive inside our bottle. Bright berry and zesty citrus so apocalyptic it will blow your system. Welcome to the new age of lemonade. It’s yuuge.
Mango, Guava, Cream
Hard Strawberry Candy

An Orange Julius style smoothie with a scoop of sherbet.

The OG style, not the DQ version, smooth, creamy orange, mixed with a sweet sherbet feel.
Just imagine savoring a moist cupcake dripping with luscious lemon icing - and having it melting in your mouth... It’s mouth watering good!
Toasted whole-grain oats, swirled with brown sugar, sweet milk, and the lightest touch of cinnamon.
This E-Juice combines juicy mangoes that just rolls across your tongue, followed by a hint of tart lychee berries for a smooth exhale.
The love child of a medium bodied tobacco and a rich, caramel chew.  Lightly toasted tobacco with a sweet caramel glaze that keeps you coming back for more.
Fill your mouth with a tropical fruit salad, heavy on sweet strawberry. Each exhale is marked by the citrus bite of lemonade on the way out.

Raspberry Pomegranate Mousse Cake: Tart and refreshing raspberry and pomegranate, combined with graham cracker crust, covered in layers of sweet vanilla cream.  All this combines for a perfect dessert juice that will leave you wanting more!
A perfect blend of gooey rich  caramel infused rice krispy with subtle note of marshmallow.
Creamy mixture of honey and savory cinnamon with a light apple aftertaste.
A smooth blend of coffee and tobacco, topped with hazelnut cream.
The notorious surge of tropical citrus that made its name in soda taps, now available for your vaping pleasure.

A sweet, fruity, and refreshing all day vape reminiscent of your favorite coffee shop iced beverage.

With spirited notes of luscious passion fruit and ripe strawberries, and a subtle twist of lemon and green tea, Passion Fruit Cooler is like an extra large red tea from your friendly neighborhood barista!
Fresh, sweet, juicy pear at it's finest. This e-liquid won Best All Day Vape at The Tucson E-Cigarette Fair May 2014.
A smooth flavor of candy apple that makes you think you’re eating a long, soft, chewy, and tangy green apple sour belt.

We have solved one of the greatest scientific mysteries of the Universe!  We have captured Dark Matter and put it in vape form! Our scientists have ascertained that it is composed of Peppermint, Chocolate & Cream :)
Our pistachio Macaroon. Sweet, complex, with hints of pistachio, vanilla & almond cookie.

Chocolate, mint and light cream. I've tried many good chocolate mint flavors in my time but often they start to lose their flavor, or become unappealing. I've attempted to craft a chocolate mint that stays refreshing and delicious for as long as you can vape it.
Sharp lemon curd topped with gooey meringue, all cradled by a thin pastry crust.

The mother of all custard. Need we say more? We start with USP grade VG infused with Madagascar vanilla. That's right! Vanilla VG made in our kitchens. We then add that to our creamy, rich custard base consisting of 3 different vanillas, 2 complex caramels, 4 different cream/milk compounds and a touch of spice.
Pineapple, Strawberry and Mango round out this delightfully fruity and sweet vape! Pineapple and Mango inhale and an awesome strawberry exhale.
The perfect strawberry daiquiri, FROZEN - loaded with fresh strawberries, a shot of rum, a spritz of lime, and triple sec.

Brace yourself for a vaping experience that is truly out-of-this-world. ANML’s Carnage will unleash the ANML in you as your taste buds go wild after vaping on this one-of-a-kind flavor. Expertly crafted by world-renowned mixologist Phillip Rocke, it tastes like delicious, strawberry candy.

This started out as a clone attempt of kryptonite by cosmic fog, but I got sidetracked and it turned out way better than I intended. It is a delicious watermelon jolly rancher type flavor that will seriously have you addicted the moment you start vaping it! Kryptonite used to be my favorite flavor and actually what got me into making my own juice, since their pricing is so freaking expensive. I have tried it several times since making my own version and I really can not vape it any more. It just doesn't taste the same anymore after vaping on the watermelon crack. There will be a slight hint of mint your first few drags, but that goes away quickly and turns into the most delectable, juicy and watermelony goodness you have ever tried! I apologize in advance for your new addiction.
Vanilla Custard
NY style cheesecake with strawberries on top

Rise and Shine No. 3 is our take on everyone's favorite fruity cereal.  There are many flavor profiles like it but ours is definitely unique. A complex blend of over 8 flavors, Fruity Cereal packs a punch of flavor that will knock you back into a hazy state of nostalgia.
Sweet juicy watermelon with a twist. On cool, its a robust watermelon with a light lime backnote.  Turn up the heat and taste a cooling lime with a juicy watermelon backnote!

Named after Europa, the smallest Galilean moon orbiting Jupiter. This moon has a water ice crust, and this flavor has an icy feel! Wild cantaloupe and Watermelon are paired with honey and an icy addition of menthol
It tastes.. SO.. DAMN.. GOOD.
A vibrant blue raspberry soda bursting with fizzy fruit goodness, and refreshing ripe raspberries.
Everything you love about sugar cookies with a tropical key lime frosting ontop

Before it became a suburban utopia, Awesometown was one massive orange grove. Introducing Orange Julius - a perfect blend of oranges, milk, and cream.

You'll love the delectable balance between ripe citrus and sweet, milky cream. This vape juice washes your whole tongue in flavor. You can taste a delicious orange at your middle palate just as the cream fills the rest of your senses.

This is one of our all-time favorites and we think you'll love it too!
Rasta Rootbeer is  soda fountain classic, creamy and sweet with a hint of sarsaparilla.
An amazing grape bubblegum
The fusion of cinnamon and apples is tried, true and dazzlingly tasty.

A rich, silky custard, homemade with a perfect balance of vanilla and baked crust.

A Noble Tradition.
A multi-layered creamy, dreamy, orange popsicle complete with a cooling sensation.

Thin mint girl scout cookies. Yes, you heard right. And yes, it's been done right. Brace yourself for your favorite childhood and adulthood treat that you can never stop craving. A thin cookie-wafer covered in a minty chocolate that will satisfy all girl scout cookie cravings!
A deliciously baked banana oatmeal cookie crust enhanced with a decadent blend of strawberry and vanilla bean ice cream. Simply the best milkshake you’ve ever had.

The original Loaded Glazed Donuts is pure bliss in a bottle.  Nothing beats the taste of a crispy, freshly baked donut straight out the kitchen, still dripping with warm glaze. Nothing except Loaded that is.

Pistachio : fresh+smooth+creamy+milky

Ratio : 70vg/30pg

Nic Levels : 0mg, 3mg, 6mg

Bottle : 100ml Chubby Gorilla
We blend our own. Something to behold. You can feel the fizz in this flavor when vaped.

This flavor took us a long time to create weighing in at 13 different ingredients this is a hugely complex dessert vape that has a nice banana, chocolate and peanut butter inhale with a smoothly sweet and creamy exhale.
The tart and tangy flavors of superfruit berries, finished with a hint of ripe green apple.

Apple and caramel have formed a long-lasting flavor partnership that can only be called a true classic. Freeman Fall Spirit apple and caramel vape juice is a dessert e-liquid flavor that tastes like a caramel apple. Who can resist a caramel apple! The candied caramel crust with the nectar sweet apple flavor. Freeman Fall Spirit brings you that delectable candied apple vape juice flavor like no one else.

Formerly known as Crunch Berry, and The Captain's Berries. Get ready for Saturday mornings again! The newly reformulated Milk & Berries is a sweet echo of every hour you spent glued to the TV enjoying your breakfast! This cereal flavor features sweet berries and creamy milk just like the Captain ordered. Enjoy this amazing new e-juice from VapeWild!

Primary Flavors: Cereal, Mixed Berries, Milk
Ice cold citrus soda blended with sweet blueberries and a splash of cold pressed lime. This is just what the doctor ordered on a hot summer day.
Refreshing, tart lemon mingled with a sweet medley of berries for a refreshing all-day treat like a cool glass of berry lemonade on a summer’s day.
Crisp Sweet Red Apple Juice. Reminiscent of your favorite boxed apple juice.
Blackberry & cucumber delight infused w/mint. Extremely refreshing.
Blueberry milk and cream, some describe it as blueberry cereal.
Iron award winner for best cereal flavor.  The perfect combination of peanut butter crunch cereal with a hint of real banana on the exhale.

Blue Raspberry Sour Candy: A sour candy lover’s dream. Tart raspberry and lemonade flavors shock the taste buds! As your mouth puckers and the flavor lingers, a sugary, fruity sweetness takes over for a wonderful finish to an exciting juice.
Freeman Minted is a particularly cool and creamy flavor. A mint chip milkshake treat that will hit your sweet spot every time.
"Slam" In goes the enchanting crunchy cereal, sprinkled with fruits from fairies. "Dunk" in a splash of delicious creamy milk from the pool of miracles.
A delicately fried doughnut sandwiched around a layer of gooey strawberry jam, with vibrant notes of cream and brown sugar. “Don’t be JELLY”

White Miso Peach, Pear, and apple: White Miso Peach Pear, and apple: A citrusy and savory ice cream with traditional Japanese flavors that trademark the country’s cuisine. Even the fruits used are traditional Japanese fair, with crisp Fuji apples, pears, and peaches forming a complex and succulent blend. Be sure to try this juice with the Eastern flair.
You've never had a vape quite like this. Bold peach and dragonfruit, with a refreshing base of green tea. Summertime right at your lips.
Taste the true perfection of a home made Georgia Pecan Pie on each draw. rich creamy notes followed by a crisp nutty pecan topped with Vanilla Whipped Cream.

Crystal Smurf is the natural progression of our original Smurf, Vapergate's #1 seller. A full flavored blue raspberry is the main profile with this juice adorned with a more subtle bouquet of additional fruits and berries beneath. Besides the lack of additional coloring of Crystal Smurf, we have refined it's vape experience. The end product tastes cleaner, vapes cleaner, and is kinder to your coils and cotton. Crystal Smurf tastes like the original but better.
This super cereal flavor is packed with a milky kick. Sure to please all the cereal lovers out there.
Rice Pudding With Cinnamon

Strawberry Limeade: When lemonade is just too boring, this flavor is the more complex upgrade. Still tart, with strawberry and lime working hand in hand, but sweet also, and very refreshing. A perfect vape to help cool off from those hot, tiring days.
A delicious blend of grape extract, with a kick of freshly picked blueberries. Naturally creating an amazing mouth watering sensation that will keep you coming back for more.
Blue Slushee

Get seduced! Fall in love with a sweet, hard candy lemon, lime, raspberry juice.

A truly unique flavor that you won't find anywhere else, consisting of the following flavors:

Main flavors:
Raspberry
Lemon
Lime

Background flavors:
Blueberry
Strawberry
This classic flavor is back and better than ever! Luscious caramel and vanilla complement this mild tobacco to make a deliciously satisfying vape.
Spiced cookies smushed into a spreadable nut butter. This vape is one decadent treat!

The Duchess’ love

Of luscious cream and caramel

Could not be for a moment denied

For all were under her spell!
A refreshingly sweet and tart lemon square. PG/VG Ratio: Max VG
Deep fried cookies and cream treats with rich chocolate and sweet filling.
Warm vanilla bakery in the inhale, rich pineapple on the exhale. Think pineapple upside down cake with the most luscious butter cream icing.
Ripe, sweet mango provides a smoothness and complexity to the comforting and refreshing flavor of home made Myer lemon lemonade.
Raspberry and Dragonfruit iced tea
Tart citrus flavor of freshly squeezed lemons infused with sweet juicy strawberries.

The trio of all trios. All Melon, combines the sweet and juicy taste of Watermelon, the smooth and crispiness of Honeydew, with the tangy and sweetness of Cantaloupe. All three melons are perfectly mixed for a melon lover’s dream. Leaving you refreshed and satisfied.

If you’re gearing up for an all night gaming marathon, then you need to be prepared!  Stock up on the great cola taste of Nuke-Q!  It gives you that extra boost of concentration!
Limited time only! Not Available at Super Duper Mart!  Don't worry, the bottle is blue, there is no added coloring in this eliquid.

A sweet, bakery kind of tobaccoish type vape. A description will never do this one justice. Some flavors are made for each other and blend perfectly. The throat hit is there, the flavor is outstanding, this is the high VG version of the original Deadly Sin. Will leave your surroundings smelling like fresh baked cookies and cakes! I have been told that this is very similar to a Crispy treat as well as Cinnamon Buns.
A distinctive blend of chocolate cookie and luscious vanilla ice cream yields a rich chocolate taste on the inhale with a captivating sweet creamy aftertaste.
House Vapor blend on the RY4; a combination of Mint & Ry4.
Load up your tanks and drip your cotton for a refreshing and satisfying bite into a fresh, crisp green apple, heartily drizzled with warm gourmet caramel.

Much like a cobra, this flavor can catch you off-guard. This juices profile is a combination of rich, milky ice cream, layered with mouthwatering strawberries, speckled with a layer of warm, fluffy cake crumbs.

PEANUT BUTTER CREAM
Take a good dollop of smooth peanut butter, a generous smudge of vanilla bean and fold together with thick, heavy cream. You’ve got that smooth, soft, luxurious Suede.
Strawberry blueberry smoothie
A smooth and flavorful hazelnut infused vanilla custard.  Notes of caramel and other nuts give a rounded and complimentary flavor to a full bodied custard.
"Start your day off right with warm blueberry vanilla waffles, sprinkled with powdered sugar, and topped off with whip cream"
What’s a blue raspberry? I have no idea, but if it actually existed, this is what it would taste like!  Sweet and tart, with a slight cooling effect.
Jusuu presents a delectable line of crisp apples, sweet peach, and juicy lychee that will leave you wanting more. Yami Vapor Juusu is presented in ultra premium packaging.
We've replaced blueberry with blackberry to give this crowd favorite a refreshing new twist.
An intense fusion of juicy peaches and strawberries that tastes like pure summertime squeezed into a bottle.
Silly rabbit, vapes are for adults. This  is a milky berry/citrus cereal that will bring you back to your childhood.
The subtle tartness of strawberries harnessed with the sweetness of shortcake, ready for conquest.
A  Pear and Coconut blend with a slight icy flavor that you wish you could be sitting on a dock by the creek vaping and fishing.

15, 30 or 120 mL of floral and herbal with an unmistakable and subtle fruitiness.

Pairs well with green tea, gin, tequila and other non aged liquors.

*All PG/VG ratios are max VG, coming in at 30/70 or higher.
Deep fried golden banana slices with butterscotch. Sweet banana, buttery cream and crunchy graham cracker notes.
The most complete Pink Starburst flavor to date, this sweet and succulent candy vape will satisfy your sweet tooth for the real thing! Plus, everyone loves the pink one!
Rich vanilla, with smooth notes of coffee and decadent whipped cream.

BEAST is a decadent and creamy pudding with just the right amount of fresh banana on top. And yes, when we say "fresh banana", we mean it. This is not that weird artificial-tasting flavor you find in banana flavored candy. Give Beast a try and see for yourself. We're sure you'll go bananas for it.

Honey Cream is a divine pairing of raw honey w/heaps of luxurious vanilla cream. The Honey Cream flavor begins w/raw honey sourced from Northern CA which is then reduced to a soluble essence & meticulously blended with natural flavors. One of the finest, smoothest vaping experiences on the planet, hands-down.
Flavor Profile: Raw honey w/premium cream.
Aged & steeped with proprietary process adding distinct notes of oak, then filtered to perfection.
80VG/20PG.
Strawberries, Watermelon, Sweet Coconut, Natilla Cream

A tangy combination of blood orange and champagne. We believe this flavor to be fit for a king...or perhaps a hand of the king.

"That's what I do: I Drink and I know things."
A warm toasted fruit tart thrown into a blender with some vanilla bean ice cream and milk
Tobacco custard

Carrot Cake is a complex blend of spices baked into a moist cake, layered with a rich cream cheese filling and topped with smooth vanilla icing.

VG/PG Ratio: 82/18
Sweet, white sugar cupcake chaos, with vanilla créme frosting. Riddled with hints of flakes that come frosted and fruit covered pebble mayhem. For the inner Anarchist in you!
Buttermilk Waffles, sweet crisp apples, cinnamon, drenched in syrup... you get the picture.  The flavor is finished off with a light cinnamon spice flavor which really compliments the profile nicely.

New Formula 3/23/17
Heisenbird is an impeccably pure rush of Blue Raspberry Slushy with a potent, sour kick. Walter has taken no half measures with this mix!
butter pecan brule
A complex blend of creams, real raspberries, and a touch of booze!
Luscious from the first to the last drop, Amazing Mango features a perfectly ripe, fresh, juicy Mango with the subtle undertones of a Peach infused cream.
Get ready to enter a state of eternal bliss with Nirvana. Nirvana is a savory blueberry donut, baked around a fluffy, moist, appetizing cake, coated with a sugary glaze.
E-juice that is so mouth wateringly delicious with its succulent blue raspberry tartness and pulled taffy sweetness, it vapes lighter than air!
"The perfect balance of fruit and decadent dessert, Orange Dream is a smooth, creamy, citrus-y blend of orange and sweet cream."
An Upside Down Vanilla Mochaccino e-Liquid. It's the best e-Juice you'll have in a long time, especially if you're looking for that Creamy Mocha flavored coffee e-Juice.

A delicious take on a classic Italian pastry. Flaky crust, layered with a vanilla cream filling, almonds, and a hint of citrus. Pair with an espresso and picture yourself in Rome outside of a little cafe on your European vacation.
A refreshing Berry Lemonade flavor!
Watermelon blasted with blueberry jelly beans.

Honey nut cereal and marshmallow smashed with the slightest amount of golden graham cracker with the tiniest hint of a ripe banana (some taste it - some don't). What was almost an abandoned project...

Our Turkish Tobacco E-liquid blend offers an excellent combination of sun-cured tobacco flavor with a very light semi-sweet top note. This unique E-liquid flavor is characteristic of the original Turkish Tobacco cultivated off the coast of the Black Sea, which is widely used in traditional cigarettes and blended into various pipe tobaccos.
A sweet cherry blossom candy, with hints of hibiscus tea and raspberry. All topped off with a sweet powdered sugar finish that’s sure to satisfy the discerning sweet tooth.
A perfectly balanced blend of your favorite fruity cereal with a splash of milk

Produced locally in Calgary, AB

Inspired by the Canadian wilderness, this flavour conjures the natural beauty of the Canadian shield, including the region’s native berries.

The inhale is so reminiscent of a forest environment that each taste is a palpable experience like being in the great outdoors

﻿Sucralose-Free:﻿ Helps make the coils last longer.

Welcome to Mother’s Milk: Suicide Bunny’s most popular juice. With a deliciously rich and creamy dessert flavor, and a light strawberry exhale, Mother’s Milk is ready to rock your world. There’s a reason our fans have voted it their favorite: once you try it, you’ll never want another.
Lightly baked apples, bakery cinnamon, subtle cake undertone.
Tart, sun bleached green apple on the inhale. On the exhale, you're treated to a rich cinnamon, creamy crust.  Just like Grandma used to make- the perfect apple pie.
A mild tobacco with menthol, perfect to help many classic smokers kick the habit.
Frosted flake wholegrain cereal with with a handful of vibrant delicious blueberries and finished with a splash of milk
Delicious Green Apple Infused Bubblegum.
Oaky bourbon with almond and coconut
Cinnamon Toast Crunch
A sweet blend of Dragon fruit, Strawberry, Vanilla custard, and Creme.
The perfect blend of orange juice and vanilla milk. Sweet, frothy and refreshing.
A delicious, refreshing summer drink with cucumber and crisp lime!

Mr. Salt-E Tobacco Mr. Salt-E is revolutionizing the fill-your-own mini e-cigarette game. Designed to offer higher nicotine levels without the rough, harsh taste and throat hit you would expect from ordinary high-nicotine e-juice,...
The tag team of a lifetime with a hit of ripe strawberries and sweet custard that'll knock you out.

From affairs of the heart to affairs of state, a rich cornucopia of tropical fruits was always the centerpiece of roman decadence. This sinfully creamy blend of banana and strawberry suggests the frolic of Satyrs and Nymphs.

We were having some trouble coming up with a name for this.  Then we saw a fat, fleecy, floating cumulonimbus cloud in the sky.  It inspired us.  What if we put a bunch of strawberries in one of those things and vaped it?  Without the gift of flight, this is the best we could do
Rich Vanilla sweet cream with a hint of cookie.

A creamy flavor like none other you've ever tasted. Mere words do not bring this flavor justice. Keylime, Strawberry, Apricot, & Vanilla Ice Cream all blended together to form an exquisite sensation for your taste buds with every breath.

Our attempt to redefine cold. Our friend Matt requested this one. Still getting his taste buds back after 30+ years of smoking, everything on the market he tried had no taste for him and he loves mint, so he requested something SUPER cold and minty. This was our prescription for him. An overload of ice, spearmint, and menthol will hit your palate as you take this one in. Just a heads up, this one is COLD.

Fried dough coated in sesame seeds and filled with a natural raspberry jam.

VG/PG Ratio: 80/20

Barrel aged for 30 days in our custom made Oak whiskey barrels.  Lemon Meringue Pie is the final release of our Brûlée line.  It is the most accurate representation of a Lemon Meringue Pie that is available in the vape community.  No corners cut, this flavor was designed with the some attention to detail as Bananas Foster and our Crème Brûlée, which have developed a cult like following since their release last year.

Cool you taste buds with Brain Freeze. This is not your typical menthol blend, Brain Freeze combines the rich flavor of strawberry, tartness of a kiwi, and sweet ruby red pomegranates. Leaving you with a very cool and satisfying exhale.
You don't have to go to Taco Bell to get your Baja fix. A sweet Mountain Dew Baja Blast style vape with a subtle coconut finish!
Strawberry ShortShake by Cheap eJuice is a strawberry milkshake cake flavored e-juice with fresh strawberries and vanilla ice cream on top of a freshly baked cake.
A sophisticated dessert blend of fruit cereal and macaroon, Pebbles boasts a powerful balance of creamy and fruit flavor with a sweet vanilla crisp on the exhale.
ShiveriNG Sheldon's bListering BLUEBERRY, ﻿frigidLy fRosTed witH a coLd heaRTed COTTON CANDY, ﻿sLoppily sLURRied iN sLeety SLUSH.
Papaya, Melon, Coconut, Rum

A true-to-its-name flavor that’s all class, with no gimmicks. Featuring a light, tangy custard filling infused with key lime, buttery graham cracker crust and a sweet, creamy condensed milk exhale, this dessert blend perfectly balances sweet, tart, and savory.
Menthol E-liquid for intense cooling during hot days or a perfect additive for any other vape.
Dark Chocolate, Peanut butter, and Cinnamon.

Castaway Coconut is Awesometown's take on a tropical vape juice. With notes of cinnamon, rum, banana and coconut, Castaway Coconut sets itself apart from other tropical vapes. You're going to want to be stranded with this flavor - pick up a bottle today!
Milk of the poppy is a delectable, complex blend of flavors. A sweet custard vape with many fruity nuances that is sure to lull you into love.
Beautifully blended blueberry and radiant raspberry mixed with a perfect peppermint.

Caramel Tobacco: We strive to provide something every vaper will be satisfied with. For our customers who love tobacco flavors, we introduce this caramel tobacco flavor. The same smoky taste you get from analogs, but with some salty sweetness added to it with the caramel flavor will satisfy the former smoker looking for something more traditional.

The Milkman's sixth offering is a fresh and sweet raspberry flavor paired with light pie cream and a crispy crumble crust. If you're looking for a light and fruity dessert flavor made with the finest ingredients and the superb attention to detail that The Milkman always delivers, you can count on Crumbleberry. To craft the best tobacco vape juice flavor, we knew it would require some conventions to be ignored. We added peanut butter and butterscotch flavor to compliment the earthy tobacco flavor tones. Trailblazer is for tobacco lovers looking to forge a new path. Very authentic, earthy complimented by a nutty density, and perfectly accented with a touch of butterscotch. Harmonious.
Orion is a delicious blend of raspberry and lemonade which create both a sweet and tangy flavor that you can't resist. There is no other like it!

Pineapple Upside Down Cake: Inspired by my great granny’s favorite dessert. Fluffy cake batter, sweet and sour pineapples, maraschino cherries, with notes of brown sugar and butter. I would eat this warm, out of the pan, before she could even flip it upside down. We hope you enjoy it just as much.

Our uniquely crafted version of the iconic Apple Pie, brings you a nostalgic experience that satisfies even those with an insatiable sweet tooth. Caramelized apples mixed into a lightly spiced cinnamon bath folded into a perfect flaky pastry crust.
An exceptional light body tobacco blend, Euro Gold's flavor profile has been painstakingly handcrafted to create the smoothest tobacco vape that truly showcases light tobacco's finest notes.

THE MILK pays homage to one of our favorite drinks, fruity cereal milk™ from [NAME REDACTED] in Brooklyn. For those that don't know, it's a drink made by steeping Fruity Pebbles in whole milk with a few other key ingredients, vigorously stirred, and strained. When [NAME REDACTED] does it, they get one of the most delicious drinks on the planet. When we do it, we get THE MILK.

PRIMARY FLAVORS: WHOLE MILK, FRUITY CEREAL, BROWN SUGAR

Foo Joo is one of the more complex flavorings that Crescent City Clouds has created. It consists of four different vanillas, four different creams, cinnamon danish, and two tobaccos. This concoction taste like no other, it hits you with a smooth vanilla in the inhale and balances out with the cream on the exhale. For those looking for a complex savory, dessert type flavor look no further.
Oh so good! Strawberries and Bananas make for the best yogurt yet!

We take this next level though, and include creamy cheesecake flavor to add some extra sweet to this sweet and salty treat.
